            <title>[LU-1887] Shrinking cur_grant_byte LBUG</title>
                <link>https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-1887</link>
                <project id="10000" key="LU">Lustre</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;Echoing 0 to &lt;b&gt;osc&lt;/b&gt;/cur_grant_bytes result to the following LBUG&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;ol&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;echo 0 &amp;gt; /proc/fs/lustre/osc/scratch-OST0003-osc-ffff88004297a000/cur_grant_bytes&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ol&gt;


&lt;p&gt;Lustre: Mounted scratch-client&lt;br/&gt;
LustreError: 4817:0:(layout.c:1528:__req_capsule_offset()) ASSERTION( offset &amp;gt; 0 ) failed: OST_SET_GRANT_INFO:setinfo_val, off=0, loc=0&lt;br/&gt;
LustreError: 4817:0:(layout.c:1528:__req_capsule_offset()) LBUG&lt;br/&gt;
Pid: 4817, comm: bash&lt;/p&gt;

